<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id744dcd7c-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s131"><num value="131">§ 131.</num><heading> National Safe Boating Week</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The President is requested to issue each year a proclamation designating the 7-day period ending on the last Friday before Memorial Day as National Safe Boating Week.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id744dcd7d-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/225">Pub. L. 105–225</ref>, <date date="1998-08-12">Aug. 12, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1260">112 Stat. 1260</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
